{"tid":1090990,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"男子葵涌飛墮平台　頭爆肢折身亡","createTime":"2019-04-04T00:24:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T00:43:16.000Z","uid":160807,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"745fb44198a0569bd7ce05141a398ceb4badcfec","tid":1090990,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T00:24:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190403/photo/bkn-20190403224639072-0403_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190404011354\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190403%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190403224639072-0403_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190404011354&h=3aff20ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n葵涌青山公路葵涌段430-436號偉賢樓，今晚(4月3日)8時許，上址平台突然傳來巨響，住客循聲查看，赫見一名男子倒臥平台昏迷，慌忙報警求助。救護員接報趕至，證實男事主已頭爆肢折，當場死亡，消防其後將遺體移至地面。 <br />\n<br />\n警方在場未有檢獲遺書，經初步調查後，相信36歲姓陳男事主由大廈天台跨過欄河，一躍而下飛墮至3樓平台，事件無可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190403/bkn-20190403224639072-0403_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190403%2Fbkn-20190403224639072-0403_00822_001.html&d=oUHbLHmoFTyfHyZ%2Brcpj5NMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=8ac19643\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190403/bkn-20190403224639072-0403_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"219fa283415eba5551f6a19f273397b34f4d9df7","tid":1090990,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T00:27:09.000Z","msg":"90%因為窮"},{"pid":"9f1980ad5a6aaed70a9be965721e2da6ee90f8ca","tid":1090990,"uid":190320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"219fa283415eba5551f6a19f273397b34f4d9df7","tid":1090990,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T00:27:09.000Z","msg":"90%因為窮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T00:33:32.000Z","msg":"唔係錢就係女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8534ead82710780e83da90b53d5c726aa4f70a5","tid":1090990,